reviewText: These dvd's DID NOT play at all! And I'm very upset

I had heard about these preachers via internet & news.  Since this DVD was made the preacher by name of Coots was bitten by Timber Rattlesnake during his church service in KY.  He & family refused treatment he died with hour or so .

I was curious how this could be done well now I know & I would not want to participate in their services or even live nearby.  Each to his own! I found this to be a very interesting documentary.
